类 StreamSourceContexts.ManualWatermarkContext<T>

    封闭类:
    StreamSourceContexts

    private static class StreamSourceContexts.ManualWatermarkContext<T>
extends StreamSourceContexts.WatermarkContext<T>
    A SourceContext for event time. Sources may directly attach timestamps and generate watermarks, but if records are emitted without timestamps, no timestamps are automatically generated and attached. The records will simply have no timestamp in that case.

    Streaming topologies can use timestamp assigner functions to override the timestamps assigned here.
